title: MUSA 5080 Portfolio for Daisy
text:
This portfolio documents my learning journey in Public Policy Analytics (MUSA 5080).


Advanced spatial analysis and data science for urban planning and public policy.




Weekly Notes: My learning reflections and key concepts
Labs: Completed assignments and analyses
Final Project: Capstone modeling challenge




I am a first-year City Planning student in Penn concentrating in urban design and transportation. I am now taking both CPLN and MUSA course that focus on both planning concepts and quantification techniques. Here is where I want to improve my visualization ability and communicating my ideas clearly to everyone




Email: yuan77@upenn.edu
GitHub: @Daisy91222
